Simple way: don't do that, for example don't check the collision or don't use the pathfinding, just wait until the player will be on the straight line to this agent.<br><br>For other situations you can use the astar <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/A*_search_algorithm" class="postlink">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/A*_search_algorithm</a> or any other the pathfinding solutions.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="https://love2d.org/forums/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=145963">darkfrei</a> — Tue Jul 05, 2022 5:36 am</p><hr />
